text: Neil Crawford (born 26 November 1958) is an English cricketer. He played 22 first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1978 and 1980. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Leeds
